    <item>
      <title>🚀 Chinese AI Company MiniMax Releases Models to Rival Industry Giants 🤖</title>
      <link>https://raf-97414.github.io/en/posts/chinese-ai-company-minimax-models/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 Jan 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://raf-97414.github.io/en/posts/chinese-ai-company-minimax-models/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;🌏 Chinese AI companies are flexing their muscles again, and MiniMax just threw down the gauntlet with &lt;em&gt;three&lt;/em&gt; new AI models! 🚀 Backed by Alibaba 🛍️ and Tencent 🎮, MiniMax has raised a cool $850 million 💰 and is valued at over $2.5 billion.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;the-models-&#34;&gt;The Models 🤖&lt;a href=&#34;#the-models-&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&lt;svg xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34;&#xA;      stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34; stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;path d=&#34;M15 7h3a5 5 0 0 1 5 5 5 5 0 0 1-5 5h-3m-6 0H6a5 5 0 0 1-5-5 5 5 0 0 1 5-5h3&#34;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&#xA;      &lt;line x1=&#34;8&#34; y1=&#34;12&#34; x2=&#34;16&#34; y2=&#34;12&#34;&gt;&lt;/line&gt;&#xA;   &lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;minimax-text-01-&#34;&gt;MiniMax-Text-01 🧠&lt;a href=&#34;#minimax-text-01-&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&lt;svg xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34;&#xA;      stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34; stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;path d=&#34;M15 7h3a5 5 0 0 1 5 5 5 5 0 0 1-5 5h-3m-6 0H6a5 5 0 0 1-5-5 5 5 0 0 1 5-5h3&#34;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&#xA;      &lt;line x1=&#34;8&#34; y1=&#34;12&#34; x2=&#34;16&#34; y2=&#34;12&#34;&gt;&lt;/line&gt;&#xA;   &lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Size&lt;/strong&gt;: A whopping &lt;strong&gt;456 billion parameters&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Skills&lt;/strong&gt;: Outperforms Google’s Gemini 2.0 Flash 🌟 on math and trivia benchmarks (e.g., MMLU, SimpleQA).&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Context Window&lt;/strong&gt;: A jaw-dropping &lt;strong&gt;4 million tokens&lt;/strong&gt; 📝 — enough to process &lt;em&gt;War and Peace&lt;/em&gt; &lt;strong&gt;five times&lt;/strong&gt; over 📚📚📚📚📚.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;minimax-vl-01-&#34;&gt;MiniMax-VL-01 👀🤓&lt;a href=&#34;#minimax-vl-01-&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&lt;svg xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34;&#xA;      stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34; stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;path d=&#34;M15 7h3a5 5 0 0 1 5 5 5 5 0 0 1-5 5h-3m-6 0H6a5 5 0 0 1-5-5 5 5 0 0 1 5-5h3&#34;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&#xA;      &lt;line x1=&#34;8&#34; y1=&#34;12&#34; x2=&#34;16&#34; y2=&#34;12&#34;&gt;&lt;/line&gt;&#xA;   &lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features&lt;/strong&gt;: Multimodal model (text + images 🖼️).&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Skills&lt;/strong&gt;: Competes with Anthropic’s Claude 3.5 Sonnet 🎭 on ChartQA but falls short of GPT-4o and InternVL2.5 on many benchmarks. 🤷‍♂️&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;t2a-01-hd-&#34;&gt;T2A-01-HD 🎤&lt;a href=&#34;#t2a-01-hd-&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&lt;svg xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34;&#xA;      stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34; stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;path d=&#34;M15 7h3a5 5 0 0 1 5 5 5 5 0 0 1-5 5h-3m-6 0H6a5 5 0 0 1-5-5 5 5 0 0 1 5-5h3&#34;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&#xA;      &lt;line x1=&#34;8&#34; y1=&#34;12&#34; x2=&#34;16&#34; y2=&#34;12&#34;&gt;&lt;/line&gt;&#xA;   &lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Talent&lt;/strong&gt;: Generates hyper-realistic speech in &lt;strong&gt;17 languages&lt;/strong&gt; 🗣️🌍 and clones voices with just &lt;strong&gt;10 seconds&lt;/strong&gt; of audio 🎧.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;open-but-not-really-&#34;&gt;Open but Not Really 🔓🤔&lt;a href=&#34;#open-but-not-really-&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&lt;svg xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34;&#xA;      stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34; stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;path d=&#34;M15 7h3a5 5 0 0 1 5 5 5 5 0 0 1-5 5h-3m-6 0H6a5 5 0 0 1-5-5 5 5 0 0 1 5-5h3&#34;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&#xA;      &lt;line x1=&#34;8&#34; y1=&#34;12&#34; x2=&#34;16&#34; y2=&#34;12&#34;&gt;&lt;/line&gt;&#xA;   &lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;MiniMax made its models available on GitHub 🐙 and Hugging Face 🧸, but…&lt;/p&gt;</description>
